dc_description_s: This metadata record describes two closely related datasets: DNR Division of Parks and Trails Area Boundaries and DNR Division of Parks and Trails District Boundaries. These datasets show the DNR Division of Parks and Trails Area and District Boundaries as of September 2010. The boundaries were created by the Division Leadership Team. Boundaries are congruent with the former Division of Trails and Waterways Area Boundaries.
dc_title_s: DNR Division of Parks and Trails Area and District Boundaries: Minnesota, 2010
